<plot>An homage to the love story genre, 'Sleepwalking' tells the tale of an extra-marital affair from the point of view of the other woman. The protagonist's internal dialogue and debate about the virtues of the relationship exposes the cyclical nature of such ill-timed connection between two people.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?501413</url></doc>
